    {
      "id": "5",
      "author": "Gaurav Shrestha",
      "role": "employee",
      "content": "Rajesh, we have identified the root cause - a storage capacity issue on our end. Our infrastructure team is working on it and we expect resolution within 2 hours. I will keep you updated.",
